Hello all,

I have be requested to make this map by a friend, who want this map in their sever. 

I took the time to make sure this was almost/close size to the portal map. I did add only a few things, which are:

* the ct spawn there a added tunnel
*added more Overlays
*added tunnels in the spawns to make it feel there is an elevator.
* added hidden ladder and ledge in the middle/center wall to go threw the hole for another route.
* added a path way in the map
*I retextured the map feel to more artistic/light feel, then just plain concerte.

Please feel free to comment and rate. 
Also tell me if there any bugs in the map and i even checked and there is none of i found on it.

Thank You and all to enjoy the new map.

Please tell all your friends to play this map on your sever and ask what they think about it, tell me what you and your buds think of it.

Later,
MOO!

aFriendlyCow
